# Wanix term bridge (not WASI stdin)

Interactive I/O for running Wanix tasks uses **`#task/‚Ä¶/term/data`** or **`#vm/<rid>/term/data`**. In ZSS, the **tape terminal tile bridge** mirrors the hidden iframe child `<wanix-term>` xterm grid while a task or VM is attached.

Raw WASI **`fd_read(0)` / `fd/0` stdin is not the integration surface** and must not be ‚Äúfixed‚Äù by patching Wanix.

## Canonical path (use this)

| Direction | Owner |
|-----------|--------|
| User input ‚Üí WASI task | `WanixTermInput` ‚Üí `sendwanixtermwrite` ‚Üí `wanixhost.ts` ‚Üí iframe child RPC ‚Üí `#task/<rid>/term/data` (line + `\n`) |
| User input ‚Üí VM serial | `WanixTermInput` ‚Üí `sendwanixterminput` ‚Üí iframe child RPC ‚Üí `#vm/<rid>/term/data` (per keystroke) |
| Task/VM output ‚Üí tile screen | iframe child `installwanixtermprobeembed` ‚Üí `zss-wanix-term-cells` ‚Üí `wanixtermscreensync` ‚Üí `WanixTermScreen` tile GPU |
| Prep / mount logs | `apilog` scrollback during spawn (not mirrored to tile) |
| Iframe spawn diagnostics ‚Üí Playwright | `postwanixiframeapilog` ‚Üí parent `zss-wanix-term-apilog` postMessage (validators). Host tape `apilog` is **not** captured by Playwright gates. |
| Routing on/off | `wanixsession` + `wanixterminalmode` (`#wanix attach` forces tile; auto-open on first cell snapshot) |
| Terminal sizing | Host pixel-sizes iframe; child FitAddon fits xterm ‚Äî see `ops/docs/wanix-term-sizing.md` |

While `iswanixtermactive()`, non-`#` lines go to the attached task or VM. WASI tasks use cyan **`wanix`** prompt; VMs use **`wanix-vm`** (raw serial). `#wanix detach` / `#wanix attach` control routing.

Wanix runs in a **hidden iframe** (`cafe/wanix-iframe-host.html` ‚Üí `wanix-iframe-host.ts`) when `#frame` is present. Boot may freeze WebGL briefly on the shared main thread.

See `ops/fixtures/wanix/README.md`. Wanix debugging: headed Playwright validators (`yarn task run wanix:vm:zed-cafe:validate`, etc.) ‚Äî not standalone HTML pages. C fixtures: rule `wanix-wasi-sdk.mdc`.

## Prohibited

- Patching **`submodules/wanix`**, **`node_modules/wanix`**, or production **`cafe/public/`** wasm paths to wire WASI stdin.
- Adding REPL fixtures that **require** `fd_read(0)` and expecting a Wanix kernel patch.
- Diagnosing ‚ÄúREPL broken‚Äù as ‚Äúenable fd_0‚Äù instead of verifying iframe term connect/spawn order and `sendwanixterminput`.
- Propagating winsize/winch/stty ‚Äî size the iframe pixels and let FitAddon fit the grid.

## Allowed

- Fixes in **`wanixhost.ts`**, `wanixtermiframehost.ts`, `wanixdrop.ts`, terminal input routing, iframe child host.
- One-shot WASI binaries that only **`fd_write`** stdout (e.g. `wasi/hello` via `wanix:wasm:build`).
- Long-running tasks for term bridge verification (`wasi/hold`, `wasi/termbridge`).

## Examples

```text
‚ùå BAD ‚Äî patch submodules/wanix/wasi/worker/worker.js to connect e.data.stdin
‚ùå BAD ‚Äî rebuild wanix for fd/0 stdin
‚ùå BAD ‚Äî serial replay path via wanixtermscreenwrite (removed; use cell snapshots)

‚úÖ GOOD ‚Äî drop termbridge.wasm, tile opens on first cell snapshot with banner text
‚úÖ GOOD ‚Äî trace sendwanixterminput + iframe spawn order in wanixtermiframehost.ts
‚úÖ GOOD ‚Äî extend headed Playwright validators in `tasks/groups/wanix.ts` (helpers in `tasks/lib/wanix/playwright-vm.ts`)
```

If interactive behavior is wrong, debug **`wanixtermiframehost.ts`** attach-on-cells, iframe sizing, and `iswanixtermactive()` ‚Äî not WASI fd 0.

VM spawn / `/zed-cafe/` in guest: rule **`wanix-vm-lifecycle.mdc`**, skills **`wanix-vm-iframe-host`**, **`wanix-zed-cafe-export`**.
